             (1.0 / NULLIF(AVG(sc.lead_time), 0)) * (1.0 - AVG(sc.defect_rate)) AS performance_score
     FROM demand_data.suppliers s
     JOIN demand_data.supply_chain sc ON s.supplier_id = sc.supplier_id

     ORDER BY performance_score DESC
     LIMIT 100
